nc=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/00v~1rpv4s9tu.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-11~e~hb32ouae.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/028ka2s-2z13q.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/01jwsbaz~~0aq.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14ea4drtqh4qw.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0xa67ouxhtyzr.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/095h7fd9rgxes.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/ticpin-logo-black.png\" as=\"image\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining. Book events, find sports venues, and discover the best dining experiences on Ticpin.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"Ticpin Team\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Ticpin,Dining,Events,Sports,Booking,Entertainment\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining.\"/><meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://ticpin.com\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Ticpin\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Ticpin | Explore Dining, Events, &amp; Play Venues\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Your ultimate gateway to world-class sports, entertainment, and dining.\"/><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" sizes=\"any\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.jpg\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/favicon.jpg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"anek_latin_235243e6-module__hdzBgW__variable inter_5f5ee935-module__rY2UjW__variable anek_tamil_c8d41f5c-module__KNtQ0G__variable anektamilcondensed_9c773438-module__lW4LeG__variable font-sans antialiased text-black overflow-x-hidden w-full\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white font-[family-name:var(--font-anek-latin)]\"><header class=\"w-full h-20 flex items-center justify-center border-b border-[#D9D9D9]\"><img alt=\"TICPIN\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"115\" height=\"32\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-8 md:h-9 object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent;width:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fticpin-logo-black.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></header><main class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 py-16 mt-[-10px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[34px] font-semibold text-black text-center mb-10 break-words\" style=\"font-family:Anek Latin\">Refund and cancellation policy</h1><div class=\"max-w-none text-[#686868] font-medium text-[18px] leading-relaxed space-y-10\" style=\"font-family:Anek Latin\"><div><p class=\"italic mb-6\">Last Updated: FEB 22, 2026</p><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold mb-4\">Important Notice</h2><p>By using the Platform and making any booking, you agree to this Policy in addition to Ticpin&#x27;s Terms &amp; Conditions and Privacy Policy. Refund and cancellation terms are determined by the Organizer and are displayed at the time of booking.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Role of Ticpin</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Ticpin acts solely as a technology intermediary that facilitates ticket bookings and reservations between customers and third-party organizers, merchants, venues, or service providers (“Organizers”).</p><p>Ticpin does not own, organize, control, or manage events, venues, or experiences listed on the Platform. All events and services are the sole responsibility of the respective Organizers.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">General Refund Principles</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Refund and cancellation terms are determined by the Organizer and are displayed at the time of booking.</li><li>By proceeding with a booking, you agree to the Organizer&#x27;s specific cancellation and refund terms.</li><li>Ticpin does not guarantee refunds unless explicitly stated.</li><li>Platform fees, convenience fees, or payment gateway charges are non-refundable, unless otherwise mentioned.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Cancellation by Customer</h2><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Events, Tickets &amp; Experiences</h3><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Customer-initiated cancellations are subject to the Organizer&#x27;s cancellation policy.</li><li>Some tickets may be non-cancellable and non-refundable.</li><li>Where cancellations are allowed, refunds (if any) will be processed after deduction of applicable charges.</li></ul></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-black font-bold\">Dining, Turf &amp; Activity Bookings</h3><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Cancellation timelines and refund eligibility vary by venue or merchant.</li><li>Late cancellations or no-shows may result in partial or zero refunds.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Cancellation or Changes by Organizer</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>If an event is cancelled, postponed, or materially changed by the Organizer, refund or rescheduling options (if any) will be communicated by the Organizer.</p><p>Ticpin shall facilitate communication and refund processing but does not control refund decisions. Refund timelines depend on the Organizer and payment gateway.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Force Majeure Events</h2><p>No refunds shall be guaranteed for cancellations or disruptions caused by events beyond reasonable control, including but not limited to natural disasters, government orders, pandemics, strikes, technical failures, or public safety concerns, unless the Organizer explicitly offers a refund.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Failed, Duplicate, or Incorrect Transactions</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>In case of a failed payment where the amount is debited but the booking is not confirmed, the amount will be reversed as per banking timelines.</p><p>For duplicate payments, eligible refunds will be processed after verification. Ticpin is not responsible for delays caused by banks or payment gateways.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Refund Processing Timeline</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Approved refunds are generally processed within 7–14 business days.</li><li>The refunded amount will be credited to the original payment method.</li><li>Ticpin does not control bank or card issuer processing timelines.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Partial Refunds</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Partial refunds may be issued in situations such as:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Partial event cancellation</li><li>Seat or service downgrade</li><li>Organizer-approved adjustments</li></ul><p>The refunded amount shall be determined solely by the Organizer.</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Non-Refundable Situations</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Refunds shall not be provided for:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Missed events or late arrivals</li><li>Incorrect bookings made by the customer</li><li>No-shows at venues or events</li><li>Tickets lost, stolen, or unused</li><li>Violation of venue or event rules</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Refund Abuse &amp; Fraud</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p>Ticpin reserves the right to:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\"><li>Deny refunds in cases of suspected fraud or abuse</li><li>Suspend or terminate user accounts involved in misuse of refund policies</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Disputes</h2><p>All disputes related to refunds or cancellations shall be resolved between the Customer and the Organizer. Ticpin may assist in communication but is not liable for the final outcome.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\">Policy Updates</h2><p>Ticpin reserves the right to modify this Policy at any time without prior notice. Updated versions will be published on the Platform and shall be effective immediately.</p></div></div><div class=\"pt-10 border-t border-zinc-200\"><h2 class=\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold mb-4\">Contact Support</h2><p>For refund-related queries or support, please contact us through the customer support channels available on the Platform or visit the <span class=\"text-black font-bold cursor-pointer\">Contact Page</span>.</p></div></div></main></div><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--><div class=\"fixed top-4 right-4 z-50 space-y-2\"></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/16pwqa5g83r6l.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:I[87236,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/028ka2s-2z13q.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/01jwsbaz~~0aq.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14ea4drtqh4qw.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0xa67ouxhtyzr.js\\\"],\\\"LoadingBoundaryProvider\\\"]\\n2:\\\"$Sreact.fragmen