 sole responsibility of the respective Organizers.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"General Refund Principles\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Refund and cancellation terms are determined by the Organizer and are displayed at the time of booking.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"By proceeding with a booking, you agree to the Organizer's specific cancellation and refund terms.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin does not guarantee refunds unless explicitly stated.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Platform fees, convenience fees, or payment gateway charges are non-refundable, unless otherwise mentioned.\"}]]}]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Cancellation by Customer\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-6\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black font-bold\",\"children\":\"Events, Tickets & Experiences\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Customer-initiated cancellations are subject to the Organizer's cancellation policy.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Some tickets may be non-cancellable and non-refundable.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Where cancellations are allowed, refunds (if any) will be processed after deduction of applicable charges.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black font-bold\",\"children\":\"Dining, Turf & Activity Bookings\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Cancellation timelines and refund eligibility vary by venue or merchant.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Late cancellations or no-shows may result in partial or zero refunds.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Cancellation or Changes by Organizer\"}],\"$L1d\"]}],\"$L1e\",\"$L1f\",\"$L20\",\"$L21\",\"$L22\",\"$L23\",\"$L24\",\"$L25\"]}],\"$L26\"]}]]}]]}]\n1d:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If an event is cancelled, postponed, or materially changed by the Organizer, refund or rescheduling options (if any) will be communicated by the Organizer.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin shall facilitate communication and refund processing but does not control refund decisions. Refund timelines depend on the Organizer and payment gateway.\"}]]}]\n1e:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Force Majeure Events\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"No refunds shall be guaranteed for cancellations or disruptions caused by events beyond reasonable control, including but not limited to natural disasters, government orders, pandemics, strikes, technical failures, or public safety concerns, unless the Organizer explicitly offers a refund.\"}]]}]\n1f:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Failed, Duplicate, or Incorrect Transactions\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"In case of a failed payment where the amount is debited but the booking is not confirmed, the amount will be reversed as per banking timelines.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"For duplicate payments, eligible refunds will be processed after verification. Ticpin is not responsible for delays caused by banks or payment gateways.\"}]]}]]}]\n20:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Refund Processing Timeline\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Approved refunds are generally processed within 7–14 business days.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"The refunded amount will be credited to the original payment method.\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin does not control bank or card issuer processing timelines.\"}]]}]}]]}]\n21:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Partial Refunds\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Partial refunds may be issued in situations such as:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Partial event cancellation\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Seat or service downgrade\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Organizer-approved adjustments\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"The refunded amount shall be determined solely by the Organizer.\"}]]}]]}]\n22:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Non-Refundable Situations\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Refunds shall not be provided for:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Missed events or late arrivals\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Incorrect bookings made by the customer\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"No-shows at venues or events\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Tickets lost, stolen, or unused\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Violation of venue or event rules\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n23:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Refund Abuse & Fraud\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin reserves the right to:\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Deny refunds in cases of suspected fraud or abuse\"}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":\"Suspend or terminate user accounts involved in misuse of refund policies\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n24:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Disputes\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"All disputes related to refunds or cancellations shall be resolved between the Customer and the Organizer. Ticpin may assist in communication but is not liable for the final outcome.\"}]]}]\n25:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold\",\"children\":\"Policy Updates\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Ticpin reserves the right to modify this Policy at any time without prior notice. Updated versions will be published on the Platform and shall be effective immediately.\"}]]}]\n26:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"pt-10 border-t border-zinc-200\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-black text-[22px] font-bold mb-4\",\"children\":\"Contact Support\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"For refund-related queries or support, please contact us through the customer support channels